&gt; &gt; That led me to think of a new term to represent the &quot;RPC over HTTP&quot; movement and which is along the spirit of the whole &quot;No SQL&quot; mantra.  &quot;No SOAP&quot; - the meaning of which is &quot;Not Only SOAP&quot;.
